    <title>[LeetCode]8.字符串转换整数(atoi)</title>
    <url>/2020/04/03/LeetCode-8-%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0-atoi/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="题目链接"><a href="#题目链接" class="headerlink" title="题目链接"></a>题目链接</h1><p><br> <a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/string-to-integer-atoi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">原题链接</a></p>
<h1 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h1><p><img src="https://github.com/qiancijun/Image/raw/master/LeetCode/8/descirbe.png" alt=""></p>
<h1 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h1><p><br>题目中有说到，该函数会根据需要丢弃无用的开头空格字符，直到寻找到第一个非空格的字符为止。所以我们先处理空白字符，直到遇到第一个非空字符。第一个非空字符如果是“-”就记录一下，最后结果乘以 -1 ，如果是别的乱七八糟的符号，直接跳过开始处理后面的数字</p>
<h2 id="数字处理的过程"><a href="#数字处理的过程" class="headerlink" title="数字处理的过程"></a>数字处理的过程</h2><p><br><img src="https://github.com/qiancijun/Image/raw/master/LeetCode/8/solve1.gif" alt=""><br><br>另外一个很关键的问题，数据溢出问题，有符号整型的数据范围在[$$-2^31$$,$$2^31$$-1]，在C语言中导入<climits>头文件用 INT_MAX 或者 INT_MIN 即可。在做每次result之前先拿INT_MAX$\color{red}{减去}$当前箭头所指的数字再除以十去和当前result做比较，这相当于一个逆运算判读是否会溢出，对result的式子做一个变换就能看出这个原理。 </p>
<h1 id="时间与内存"><a href="#时间与内存" class="headerlink" title="时间与内存"></a>时间与内存</h1><p><img src="https://github.com/qiancijun/Image/raw/master/LeetCode/8/pass.png" alt=""></p>
<h1 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h1><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">myAtoi</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-built_in">string</span> str)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> result = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> len = str.size();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i, sign = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-built_in">isspace</span>(str[i]); ++i); <span class="hljs-comment">//跳过开头空白字符</span><br>    sign = (str[i] == <span class="hljs-string">'-'</span>) ? <span class="hljs-number">-1</span> : <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">// 记录负号</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(!<span class="hljs-built_in">isdigit</span>(str[i]) &amp;&amp; str[i] != <span class="hljs-string">'-'</span> &amp;&amp; str[i] != <span class="hljs-string">'+'</span>)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">//第一个非空字符不是数字或正负号</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(str[i] == <span class="hljs-string">'-'</span> || str[i] == <span class="hljs-string">'+'</span>)<br>        ++i; <span class="hljs-comment">//跳过正负号</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(result = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; <span class="hljs-built_in">isdigit</span>(str[i]); ++i)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> digit = str[i] - <span class="hljs-string">'0'</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(result &gt; (INT_MAX - digit) / <span class="hljs-number">10</span>)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> sign == <span class="hljs-number">-1</span> ? INT_MIN : INT_MAX; <br>        &#125;<br>        result = result * <span class="hljs-number">10</span> + digit;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> result * sign;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><br>若有问题或者疑问，欢迎加Q探讨</p>
]]></content>
